Package model

Class Inventory

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Inventory
  • public class Inventory
extends java.lang.Object
    Inventory class that depends on the Part and Product classes. This class handles two separate lists, one for all part objects created in the program and another for all product objects created in the program. These lists are displayed in two separate tables inside the main screen of the program.

    The class has multiple methods that perform the following: Retrieving all objects in a list. Auto-generating an id for a part object or a product object. Adding an object to a list. Retrieving an object or objects from a list. Updating objects in a list. Deleting objects in a list.
